---

<section
    class="relative h-[95vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-20"
>
    <img
        alt="Costa Peruana waves"
        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
        src="/images/hero.webp"
        fetchpriority="high"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-gradient"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6"
        >
            <span class="text-primary material-symbols-rounded text-sm"
                >water_drop</span
            >
            La mejor experiencia de surf en Perú
        </div>

        <h1
            class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl mb-6 drop-shadow-2xl leading-tight"
        >
            Descubre la Magia de la <span class="text-primary"
                >Costa Peruana</span
            >
        </h1>

        <p
            class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed"
        >
            Olas perfectas, playas vírgenes, gastronomía de clase mundial y
            aventuras inolvidables te esperan. Vive la experiencia definitiva
            del surf en Perú.
        </p>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16"
        >
            <button
                class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-orange-600 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group shadow-xl shadow-orange-900/40"
            >
                Explorar Aventuras
                <span
                    class="material-symbols-rounded group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                    >arrow_forward</span
                >
            </button>
            <button
                class="w-full md:w-auto bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-white/20 transition-all"
            >
                Ver Destinos
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <p
                class="text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold"
            >
                Descubre más
            </p>
            <span
                class="material-symbols-rounded animate-bounce mt-2 text-white/40"
                >expand_more</span
            >
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
